<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; In my capacity of User Support for the OSG, I have a need to be</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; able to</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; run automated tests which obtain VOMS proxy credentials based on DOE</font>
